<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='854962' id='t-854962'>I was able to end my own crazy love story</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='858406' id='t-858406'>by breaking the silence.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='860607' id='t-860607'>I'm still breaking the silence today.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='863122' id='t-863122'>It's my way of helping other victims,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='866938' id='t-866938'>and it's my final request of you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='870306' id='t-870306'>Talk about what you heard here.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='873138' id='t-873138'>Abuse thrives only in silence.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='876466' id='t-876466'>You have the power to end domestic violence</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='880169' id='t-880169'>simply by shining a spotlight on it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='883678' id='t-883678'>We victims need everyone.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='886752' id='t-886752'>We need every one of you to understand</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='890825' id='t-890825'>the secrets of domestic violence.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='894603' id='t-894603'>Show abuse the light of day by talking about it</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='897587' id='t-897587'>with your children, your coworkers,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='899714' id='t-899714'>your friends and family.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='901651' id='t-901651'>Recast survivors as wonderful, lovable people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='905097' id='t-905097'>with full futures.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='907912' id='t-907912'>Recognize the early signs of violence</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='911393' id='t-911393'>and conscientiously intervene,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='914226' id='t-914226'>deescalate it, show victims a safe way out.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='918388' id='t-918388'>Together we can make our beds,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='922383' id='t-922383'>our dinner tables and our families</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='926000' id='t-926000'>the safe and peaceful oases they should be.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='929257' id='t-929257'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
